The Dagger of Delight is an ordinary [items]dagger[/items], however 1/day you may touch a target with the dagger and gain [rules]Advantage[/rules] with them for 1 minute on any d20 checks using Charisma. This ability of the item resets each dawn.

You may use a [action]Utilize[/action] action rather than an [action]Attack[/action] action to gain Advantage when touching the target. The target is unaware of your advantage.
